Campfire
========

Campfire service hook allows you to post commit updates into the chat room.

Install Notes
-------------

  1. subdomain is your campfire subdomain
	(ie 'your-subdomain' if you visit 'https://your-subdomain.campfirenow.com')
  2. room is the actual room ID, not the name
  3. token is your API token. get it from campfire's "Edit my Campfire
     account" screen
  
Configuration
-------------

    campfire:
      subdomain: foo (if your url is foo.campfirenow.com)
      api_token: YOUR_API_TOKEN
      room: ROOM_ID